Alembic migrations for Lumora.

The database URL and target metadata are sourced from the application at runtime
(see env.py), so you do not set sqlalchemy.url in alembic.ini.

Run from the backend/ directory:

  # generate a migration from model changes
  alembic revision --autogenerate -m "describe change"

  # apply migrations
  alembic upgrade head

For the SQLite MVP, batch mode is enabled automatically so ALTER operations work.
